Privacy Policy Statements
The "MyWorldWeather" mobile app ("the app") was developed and maintained by the Hong Kong Observatory (HKO) on behalf of the World Meteorological Organization (WMO). The HKO records visits to the app without collecting any personal identifiable
      information from users. Records are collected to compile statistical reports and diagnose problems with, or concerning, computer systems to help improve the app.
User's location may be determined in the app to provide location-based weather service. No personal identifiable information from users is collected. Users cannot be identified from this information and it is only used to assist us in improving the app.